arya stark aesthetic

title: Jonrya Reunion
body: I want to see them hug again more than anything. I want to hear Jon call Arya little sister like in the books. I want to see the looks on their faces when they see each other again. They have such a strong bond in the books and on the show, we saw a little of that in season one. I want to explore that more as much as possible. Maybe I’m looking for too much, but I want it. I want to see Kit and Maisie together on screen again. And I am SO excited to see how it will all be pulled off on screen.
